{"tid":501091,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母廢老死返屋企訓啦","createTime":"2017-12-16T13:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T15:14:18.000Z","uid":142151,"like":56,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"751863657840763c573a90199bb3d33fc48feb09","tid":501091,"uid":142151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"頭先係人生距離死亡最近既一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟係外國揸26 頭先揸山路<br />\n轉緊一個盲彎 突然見到有部46 u-turn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻收油 點知對頭有部泥頭車為左避佢而cut過黎線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見唔夠位即刻向路邊訓低左部車<br />\n成個人即仆左落地<br />\n手先落地之後下巴...<br />\n好彩有手套同full face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企起身之後部泥頭車走左<br />\n泥頭車後面部車停左係路邊<br />\n見我起到身都走埋<br />\n個U-turn廢老落車望住我 <br />\n指住屌佢祖宗十八代<br />\n佢仲同我講無U-turn <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩人同車都無咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但宜家諗返真係覺得好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打出黎只係想發洩下<br />\n多謝睇曬既巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091e7860576ed692bb23f2899f7518eb6142c9e2","tid":501091,"uid":157521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"最緊要人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01502cec485bf5a3c6ffa49a45be583e8cf36b5","tid":501091,"uid":142151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩先返到屋企驚到震<br />\n訓左一覺心情平穩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/a