rmal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095b1975cd761aede50e54b34edaffabc15def43","tid":501091,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:21:04.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死廢老 好撚心撘uber<br />\n阻撚住曬 係快線揸55 mph<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> limit寫70<br />\nCut線又唔撚睇 <br />\n白人廢老阻到地球轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錯又唔撚認 <br />\n之前有朋友俾個廢老呀婆hit &amp; run<br />\n當時就認錯  點知之後同保險講話係我朋友撞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩搵到cam影到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc24dd040927dd2ef9cac2a69061101b2eb30a9","tid":501091,"uid":39709,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T23:08:25.000Z","msg":"電單車撚,快D俾車車死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53bd77cd692c9d6abb10e5b5dcafbff52fd7096","tid":501091,"uid":22005,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電單車撚,快D俾車車死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你生癌仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7820d827d7ae702a8ccc8a43c56b5875394136c9","tid":501091,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野26 46<br />\n打兩個轆 四個轆 唔撚得？<br />\n屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n廢老出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}